{"tid":1240961,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"真係好撚攰","createTime":"2019-06-18T13:57:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T14:28:01.000Z","uid":175748,"like":117,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"b77ebb7e08b24751453c16bf632c34076e250f48","tid":1240961,"uid":175748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T13:57:44.000Z","msg":"呢。2個禮拜真係精神攰，身體攰<br />\n69遊行，612請假去吸煙（有受傷），616遊行去曬<br />\n番工仲要無乜心機，成日要mon住事態發展<br />\n今日老闆問我公事問我個客覆咩野，我個陣睇緊記者會<br />\n我講左一句都係未撤回<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，個個都㩒住嘴笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我都好想出一分力，但好認真21/6出左<br />\n我一定出唔到23/6，真係好需要休息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我相信真係唔少人都係咁諗<br />\n我真係覺得23/6 同1/7 兩者取其一出黎會比較適合<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />集氣一日，長期作戰要休息<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />兩日都行，死廢柴咁都頂唔順"},{"pid":"c2f215eb17d646a9d34fca9a9e6c76d9f399272f","tid":1240961,"uid":82640,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T13:58:20.000Z","msg":"集會咪撚行啦屌佢老味"},{"pid":"7891bef5db26ceb68b5c01a9aaaad9ede8b4c52f","tid":1240961,"uid":2864,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T13:59:44.000Z","msg":"體力透支<br />\n訓極都唔夠"},{"pid":"ec713b84551915193cb135c2a06c2967cbe4dc84","tid":1240961,"uid":22700,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T13:59:56.000Z","msg":"個個星期都出去真係好攰...鄭月娥正仆街"},{"pid":"1b36f20e2e76da9eb730371307b15d035d9151b2","tid":1240961,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:00:01.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n<br />\n我會揀 71,  因為差不多全港市民都知有 71<br />\n<br />\n我都攰"},{"pid":"398dd3223e6b9acf3b387b8d6b796ded528ad8eb","tid":1240961,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1b36f20e2e76da9eb730371307b15d035d9151b2","tid":1240961,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"rep