ji\" />義士以死明志，200萬人和平上街政府都繼續堅持。群眾甚至比多幾日時間政府出黎回應群眾，而家壓力應該係政府到，群眾要做既野就係靜待政府回應+準備。唔係又係度又諗其他方案<br />\n<br />\n大家唔好比人SPIN到</span></span>"},{"pid":"3635edda4d27d5c2e542fa2356d959f801d00685","tid":1240961,"uid":263730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:05:29.000Z","msg":"真係好撚攰，平時太廢青，做左三日運動之後，透支曬體力。呢兩日返工都抖唔到氣咁<br />\n個政權可唔可以比我地抖抖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我之後會訓練返體力架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f18b9189a3042e3a56489c512e3b66b5e9fcb728","tid":1240961,"uid":78559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:07:07.000Z","msg":"呢幾日keep住攰，<br />\n身攰心都更攰<br />\n留唔離開部手機，係咁睇連登"},{"pid":"5acc278ec2adfdf59d3d2a9c46961b966bcc5f73","tid":1240961,"uid":182195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:07:29.000Z","msg":"休息下先啦<br />\n近日應該較少新發展"},{"pid":"a8b9fe3829effe03db3502c88f0c6b18e1f39b97","tid":1240961,"uid":144883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:07:44.000Z","msg":"咁就攰？有d人話要個個星期日出黎遊行永續社運㗎"},{"pid":"28ad04024d0d00d683d5e658e1641cc91d9c2cb7","tid":1240961,"uid":45206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:08:29.000Z","msg":"月尾有國歌法 又人工島<br />\n會攰到你仆街<br />\n不如一次過講真普選 一次ko所有問題算啦"},{"pid":"feac5f95c2ab61296c47be48fb17c9f14a5fdc63","tid":1240961,"uid":244332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:08:34.000Z","msg":"原來咁多人都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"320741da3e801c6b396a12c85987e537d05e41f3","tid":1240961,"uid":45206,"like":1,"dislike":0,"